---
title: Veggie Chili Mac and Cheese with Corn and Sweet Peppers
description: Turn on the game and jump into your comfy clothes for tonight's combination of our two favourite winter meals. Chilli mac and cheese brings two worlds together for an uber tasty dinner the whole family can root for!
